<section class="section about-bio">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="bio-layout">
        <div class="bio-image">
            <img src="/images/gera-headshot.jpg" alt="Gera Yeremin" class="headshot" />
        </div>
        <div class="bio-content">
            <h2 class="section-title">Developer + Marketer + Business Owner</h2>
            <p class="text-xl">
                Most developers don't understand P&L. Most marketers can't build product. I do both.
            </p>
            <p>
                I've been building software for 15+ years and running marketing for almost as long. I co-founded 57 Seconds, a digital agency, where I build the tools we use to help clients.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>I eat my own dog food.</strong> The booking system, the reporting dashboards, the automationâ€”I build them for my own business first. If it doesn't make money or save time, I don't write the code.
            </p>
            <p class="signature">- Gera Yeremin</p>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
    .bio-layout {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: var(--space-12);
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .bio-image {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        width: 300px;
        position: relative;
    }

    .headshot {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-lg);
        transform: rotate(-2deg);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .headshot:hover {
        transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1.02);
    }

    .bio-content {
        flex: 1;
    }

    .bio-content .section-title {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .text-xl {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: var(--color-text);
        font-weight: 500;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .bio-content p {
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .signature {
        font-family: 'Nothing You Could Do', cursive, sans-serif; /* Fallback */
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--color-accent);
        margin-top: var(--space-4);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .bio-layout {
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            gap: var(--space-8);
        }

        .bio-image {
            width: 200px;
        }

        .bio-content .section-title {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
        }
    }
</style>
